node.text: @ScoutBassett’s determination on the track is as inspiring as her commitment to mentoring young athletes with disabilities, teaching them to reach beyond societal barriers. Watch Scout #LeadWithLove in this film. #PGPartner #ChangeStartsWithSport
Thank you so much for sharing my journey and helping me to lift up more girls along the way 💙
